    <ThingDef ParentName="AA_PseudoBaseMechanoid">
        <defName>AA_WaywardMobileAssembler</defName>
        <label>wayward mobile assembler</label>
        <description>An automated, mobile mechanoid factory. Mobile assemblers are used by mechanoids to convert organic matter into useable stuff, such as building materials, munitions and explosives. This particular assembler seems to be lost and wandering aimlessly. It can be "tamed" and kept in check by the colony, since it is not sentient and lacks any concept of friend or foe.\n\nA wayward mobile assembler is very low maintenance, since it is resistant to damage, feels no pain, hovers over terrain, needs no rest whatsoever and can't get sick (lacks any organic components). It will however need to consume organics to power its internal batteries. It also lacks any kind of sentience, so it won't even flee from combat if attacked.</description>
